tafsir[26]{c,v,t}:
  37,77,"Men daЙ—ndi Й“eynguure makko makko nden e gomЙ—imЙ“e mo Й“en tun. ЖҒeya kan, Men yooliri Й“eya keeferaaku maЙ“Й“e ngun."
  37,78,"Men heddinani mo e mofte hikkotooЙ—e Й—en, mantoore moЖҙЖҙere, nde Й“e mantirta mo."
  37,79,"Nuuhu hisii o daЙ—ii wowleede bone, e mofte sakkitiiЙ—e Й—en. Wurin, mantoore e jantoore moЖҙЖҙere, heddoto fii makko."
  37,80,"Ko sugu ndii njoЙ“di, ndi Men warjorii Annabi Nuuhu, woni ko Men warjorta moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e dewe mun Й—en, Й“e rewi Alla tun."
  37,81,"Kanko Nuuhu, ko o jeyanooЙ—o e jeyaaЙ“e Amen gomЙ—imЙ“e, woni e Й—oftaare Alla Й“en."
  37,82,"Refti Men yooliri hedditiiЙ“e Й“en, waame mbo Men wurti e maЙ“Й“e on. ЖҒe fow maЙ“Й“e Й“e gasi."
  37,83,"Awa Ibraahiima, ko jeyanooЙ—o e jokkuЙ“e diina makko, rewi laawol makko ka wootinЙ—ingol Alla."
  37,84,"Janto nde o ardunoo ka Joomi makko, Й“ernde hisunde e sirku, laaЙ“anЙ—o Alla e tagu Makko ngun."
  37,85,"Nde o maakannoo baaba makko e yimЙ“e mun sirkaynooЙ“e Й“en: Ko honЙ—um rewton gaanin Alla?"
  37,86,"E ko reweteeЙ—i fefindaaЙ—i, faalaЙ—on rewude ko wanaa Alla?"
  37,87,"Ko sikkuЙ—on, onon yimЙ“e am, e Joomiraawo tageefo ngon, si on hawroyii e Makko, hara on rewaano Mo? Ko sikkuЙ—on O gollata on ontuma?"
  37,88,"Annabi Ibraahiima ndaariri ka koode, himo taskoo Й—aЙ“Й“a feere, no daЙ—ira yaltidugol e maЙ“Й“e."
  37,89,"O ngantinori yaltidugol e yimЙ“e makko Й“en ka iidi maЙ“Й“e, wiide: ko mi nawnuЙ—o."
  37,90,"ЖҒe acci mo caggal Й—on, Й“e hucciti."
  37,91,"O moltii e reweteeЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in gaanin Alla, o jalnori Й—i maakugol: E on Гұaamataa ko sirkanooЙ“e on Й“en moЖҙЖҙinani on kon?"
  37,92,"Ko heЙ“i on, on wowlataa, on jaabotaako? Ko sugu Й—um Й—oo rewetee gaanin Alla?"
  37,93,"Ibraahiima moltorani Й—i, piyirgol Й—i junngo makko Гұaamo ngon, fii muncugol Й—i."
  37,94,"RewaynooЙ“e Й—in sanamuuji Й“en, fewri ka makko, hiЙ“e yaawno."
  37,95,"Ibraahiima fewtitiri Й“e tabitaal, o feli Й“e, o maaki: E on reway kon ko lesirЙ—on juuЙ—e mon, accon Alla?"
  37,96,"Ko Alla tagi on, O tagi golle mon Й—en, wano Й—in sanamuuji Й—i leston. Ko Kanko tun hanndi e Mo rewon, hara on renndidaani Mo e goЙ—Й—um goo."
  37,97,"Nde Й“e ronkunoo teeЙ—oragol mo hujja, Й“e yahri doole, Й“e diisonsiri haa Й“e fottani ko Й“e waЙ—ata ibraahiima; Й“e wi'i: mahanee mo maadi, hebbiniron ndi carma, huЙ“Й“on Й—e yiite, refti buЙ—on mo ton."
  37,98,"YimЙ“e Annabi Ibraahiima Й“en faandanii mo bone, no Й“e gaynira fii makko,Й“e Й“oortondira e makko, kono Men waЙ—i Й“e kamЙ“e sooyuЙ“e Й“en; nde Men waЙ—annoo mo yiite ngen Й“uuЙ“ol e kisiyee."
  37,99,"Ibraahiima maaki: Min on, ko mi feroowo ka Joomi am, mi yalta e leydi yimЙ“e am Й“en, no mi heЙ“ira feere rewugol Mo; aray nde O fewnata lam e ko moЖҙЖҙanta lam aduna e laakara."
  37,100,"Joomi am, arsikam Й“iЙ—Й—o moЖҙЖҙo, ko wallitoo lam, semmbina lam e yimЙ“e am Й“en, tuma mi ferata."
  37,101,"Men jaabiniri toraare makko nden, humpitugol mo ko welata mo, fewndo Men wewlinirnii mo geЙ—aljo mawnoowo, muГұГұoytooЙ—o; on woni Ismaa'iila (yo o his)."
  37,102,"Nde Ismaa'iila mawnunoo, o yottodi e ben makko jahal, ben makko Ibraahiima hoyЙ—i, koyЙ—ol AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en non, ko wahayu. O humpiti geЙ—al makko wiide mo: ko an yo Й“iЙ—Й—o am, mi yi'ii e koyЙ—ol, wonnde miЙ—o hirse. Ndaaru ko yi'uЙ—aa e Й—um. Ismaa'iila jaabii baaba'en mun, wiide: Baaba'en, waЙ—ee ko yamiraЙ—on kon fii hirsugol lam, on taway lam, si Alla jaЙ“ii, jeyaaЙ—o e muГұooЙ“e e weltorЙ“e Гұaawoore Alla nden."
